text: Kiichiro Toyama (22 November 1909 - 15 September 1999) was a Japanese gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1909 births Category:1999 deaths Category:Japanese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Japan Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
